ce` region being unavailable.\n\n### Output JSON\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"Region is unavailable\",\n    \"rpc error\",\n    \"failed to retrieve product\",\n    \"failed to get product recommendations\",\n    \"failed to complete the order\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Failures querying products due to Error 9005: Region is unavailable.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to query product by id: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Cascading errors in product retrieval and order completion due to region unavailability in productcatalogservice.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to get product recommendations: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nThe presence of `Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable` suggests a significant service disruption potentially related to backend infrastructure or configuration issues affecting data retrieval pertinent to frontend requests. Further investigation into backend region availability and connectivity is recommended to pinpoint and resolve the originating cause.", "trace_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"error_region_unavailable\",\n    \"status_500\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant latency spikes and error 'Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable'\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Anomaly duration increased from ~10ms to ~38s across multiple calls\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Downstream impact from productcatalogservice causing multiple 500 errors\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Status code 500 observed in combination with delays in communication with productcatalogservice\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Error propagation detailed in failed order preparation involving productcatalogservice\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService failed to retrieve product details due to 'Region is unavailable'\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"memory_usage\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt_max\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"The service experienced a drastic increase in error_ratio across multiple pods (e.g., shippingservice-0 and shippingservice-1), with median values changing from 0.0 to 60.0.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio for shippingservice-0: 0.0 -> 60.0, shippingservice-1: 0.0 -> 60.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Multiple frontend pods encountered an increased error_ratio and server_error_ratio, with median ratios changing to levels between 17.92% and 28.57%.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"server_error_ratio for frontend pods increased to the range of 17.92%-28.57%.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"The service observed very high latency spikes in rrt_max, with the median value leaping from 13.2k to over 402M.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max for productcatalogservice-1: 13276 -> 40274437.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
